body:
This is notify you that you are  among the last quarter recipients to be paid the scam  victims  compensation of $2.5M this year 2023 by United Nations ,World Bank , International monetary fund (IMF),Federal bureau of investigation and the inter-pol in collaboration with the  Central bank of Nigeria . You are  hereby  required  to pay the last fee of $175 to facilitate  the immediate  transfer of your fund.
Regards
Franklin Chamberlain

subject: Re:   This is notify you that you
body:
Hello Franklin,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm thrilled to hear about this opportunity! Could you please provide more details? For instance, what is the purpose of this fund and how was I selected as a recipient?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Gaston
